metadata.name: Pendente Tower
metadata.description:
This image has been taken during a wander around the iconic Torre Pendente in Pisa. This moment turns into something supernatural when the clouds came to show up just in a perfect alignment with the famous Leaning Tower. The moody light created at this point a somewhat divine moment giving even more magnificence to the tower with this perspective.

Artist : Romain Gandr√©
Year of Creation : 2021
Place : Pisa, Italy
Edition : 1/1
Size : 4900 px on the long end
